TEXT.S: Kolinda Grabar-Kitarović 4 bulad 29 demiad, Kolinda Grabar-Kitarović, u misingkiway. 1968 a mihca nalecuhan) u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (congtung) nu Croatia ayza sa ci Kolinda Grabar-Kitarović, micakat a demiad sa i 2015 a mihca 2 bulad 19 demiad. Her presidential term ended on 18 February 2020.
